                               Introduction
                               ~~~~~~~~~~~~



  This archive contains new images for GoldEd4 toolbars.

  There are toolbars for some GoldEd-packet (envSTM, envTEX, hexedit)
  and some images for .... what ever you want.

  Let's have a look at the images:


  @{"hexedit images" system "sys:utilities/multiview pics/hexedit.iff"}

  @{"stormc images" system "sys:utilities/multiview pics/stormc.iff"}

  @{"texserver images" system "sys:utilities/multiview pics/texserver.iff"}

  @{"other images" system "sys:utilities/multiview pics/other.iff"}


  >>>@{" " link 2} Installation

  >>>@{" " link 3} Author


@endnode

@node 2 "Installation"
@toc main


                               Installation
                               ~~~~~~~~~~~~



  ..seems to be very easy...



  - backup your old toolbar images

  - copy the contents of the archive dir toolbar into your GoldEd:toolbar dir

  - set the number of colours to 256 (8 bit)

  - change the colour of toolbar to white



  ...that's all folks...isn't it easy, isn't it...have fun with this stuff...



  no warranties - of course


  The images are free to use for personal items!


  >>>@{" " link 3} Author

@endnode

